\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line Global Training \'28Pty\'29 Ltd t\'2Fa Prestige Academy is registered with the Department of Higher Education and Training and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC.  \line \line The Diploma in Executive Management Assistant programme was tabled at Accreditation Committee meeting of  24 March 2011 and it was not accredited for the following reasons\'3A\line \line The programme design is inadequate to achieve the purpose of a programme of this nature. For example\'2C the programme does not allow sufficiently for horizontal or vertical alignment and progression appears to be problematic. In addition\'2C certain modules which are deemed fundamental for this programme are also omitted.   \'28Criteria 1\'29\line \line Not all staff members teaching on the programme hold the required level of qualification and have the requisite experience \'28Criteria 3 and 4\'29.\line \line The institution submitted a representation. \cell \pard 

